snippet.title: AERIM AMBER MUSK D'OR PERFUME REVIEW | A CLASSY FRAGRANCE THAT WILL MAKE YOU FEEL LIKE A BOSS BABE
snippet.description:
Hello my lovelies, in this video I'm sharing a review of the Aerim Amber Musk D'or of the Private Perfume Collection, this is a super classy fragrance, that will make you feel rich and like a total boss babe!

AERIN Beauty is a luxury fragrance brand inspired by the signature effortless style, aesthetic point of view, and heritage of its founder, Aerin Lauder.

More info:
